03:14.680 --> 03:21.760
what did I do in the past half an hour? That's your brain on automatic pilot. Another example,

03:22.000 --> 03:30.400
many of you right now are listening to me on automatic pilot. And I know who you are.

03:35.440 --> 03:39.040
Now, here's the thing. If your brain is an automatic pilot, this leads to what a scientist

03:39.040 --> 03:47.120
called mental myopia, also known as tunnel vision. And if you have tunnel vision, that's a bit of a

03:47.120 --> 03:52.480
problem because it confuses people about our own performance. And this is the reason that many

03:52.480 --> 03:59.040
people go through life acting like a mediocre race car driver who sits in his car, looks in his

03:59.040 --> 04:04.320
